  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935830/extras/3d3cb8d9be737602adfb81611ce8f7ca.webp?t=1734973313\" width=615 height=36 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935830/extras/ce1ad8d41379a7df6053d525fcd55cd3.apng?t=1734973313\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935830/extras/ce1ad8d41379a7df6053d525fcd55cd3.poster.avif?t=1734973313\" class=\"bb_img\" width=605 height=32 /></picture></span><br><i>A mysterious evil-doer has emerged from the unknown to create a sinister new world. With nobody else left to defeat him, it is on you and any other misguided souls you stumble upon to put an end to his dastardly plot.</i><br><br>Jump, fly and race through several lands - from the sunny oasis of the Diamond Desert, to the gloomy swamps of the Mystic Stormlands - to save the world from the most dangerous weapon ever constructed.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935830/extras/16337935585eef5168ca70a24d730dc8.webp?t=1734973313\" width=615 height=36 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935830/extras/c842a8cbfb9abe8b619c732a76ec4773.apng?t=1734973313\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935830/extras/c842a8cbfb9abe8b619c732a76ec4773.poster.avif?t=1734973313\" class=\"bb_img\" width=605 height=26 /></picture></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935830/extras/22098fbb1139c6bdfb1dd602eab8df4c.webp?t=1734973313\" width=10 height=10 /></span> 6 Playable Characters with unique powers and abilities.<br><span 